column5: Tossing up the idea of camping this weekend,just wondering where to go.......Anybody heading to Quinte this weekend???Let us know where you go.........thx..... Chuck and Shelley...........
Hey there Chuck  Im heading to the Pool saturday.  Have a great weekend bud.
Wherever you go Chuck, catch a lot. Quinte would be a good idea though.
Chuck. you fine folk have a PM

Hey chuck i was on the phone with ontario out of doors writer bob mgary,and he said the walleyes,and buckets have been on fire this week,all around the trenton area,good catches of 3-5lb walleyes & largies,if i wasnt already commited to salmon fishing this weekend thats where i would be going......just a little bit of info for you....cheers    just thought it might make your decision a little easier...
Hey Fishndevil is the Bob McGary the ex Principal I remember in High Scholl he ran our Fishing Club. WHat a great guy he is.  Cheers
